```
useradd -m -g users -G wheel -s /usr/bin/bash username
```
* `-m` 相当于`--create-home`,create the user's home directory if it does not exist 

* `-g`相当于`--gid GROUP`, the group ID for a new user's initial group

* `-G`相当于`--groups GROUP1[GROUP2..]`,A list of supplementary groups which the users is also of a member of

* `-s`相当于`--shell SHELL`,the name of user's login shell